1. *Žalostan* sam zbog gubitka prijatelja. (I am *sad* due to the loss of a friend.)
2. Ova *žalostna* melodija me podsjeća na moju baku. (This *melancholy* melody reminds me of my grandmother.)
3. Moramo izraziti *žalost* zbog njihovog gubitka. (We need to express our *condolences* for their loss.)
4. Osjetila je duboku *žalost* nakon raskida veze. (She felt a deep *sadness* after the break-up.)
5. Njihova smrt je uzrokovala *žalost* u cijelom gradu. (Their death caused *grief* throughout the city.)
6. *Žalosno* je vidjeti toliko ljudi bez doma. (It is *sad* to see so many people without homes.)
7. Naša *žalost* ne može se usporediti s njihovim gubitkom. (Our *sorrow* cannot compare to their loss.)
8. U njegovom glasu bila je neka *žalostna* nota. (There was a certain *melancholic* note in his voice.)